# Code owners for backblaze-labs/b2-action
#
# These owners will be automatically requested for review on any PR.
# Order matters: the LAST matching pattern takes most precedence.
#
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/managing-repository-settings/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
# TODO: replace `@backblaze-labs/maintainers` with the real team or user handle
# once the repo is hooked up to the Backblaze GitHub org. A team handle is
# preferred over an individual so reviews don't block on one person being out.
*                               @backblaze-labs/maintainers

# Build / release infrastructure: extra scrutiny because a broken release
# workflow can publish a broken Action to millions of consumers.
/.github/workflows/release.yml  @backblaze-labs/maintainers
/.github/workflows/ci.yml       @backblaze-labs/maintainers
/dist/                          @backblaze-labs/maintainers
/action.yml                     @backblaze-labs/maintainers
/package.json                   @backblaze-labs/maintainers

# Security policy edits require a security-aware reviewer.
/SECURITY.md                    @backblaze-labs/maintainers
